    "This approach can help circumvent the generality and superficiality of some AI responses.",
    "• Develop Prompt Engineering Skills: Teach students the principles of prompt engineering to enhance the quality of AI-generated answers.",
    "This involves refining questions to be clear, direct, and contextually rich.",
    "• Foster Analytical Skills: Encourage students to critically analyze AI responses, identifying biases, inaccuracies, or superficiality.",
    "This process can be an excellent opportunity for classroom discussion and debate."
